ependentClass;\n                try (HeapByteBufferArrayBaseOffsetRestorer ignored =\n                             HeapByteBufferArrayBaseOffsetRestorer.zeroOffset()) {\n                    platformDependentClass = Class.forName(\n                            \"io.netty.util.internal.PlatformDependent\",\n                            true,\n                            classLoader\n                    );\n                }\n                exerciseInitializedPlatformDependent(platformDependentClass);\n                exerciseCachedDirectBufferConstructor(classLoader);\n            } catch (Error error) {\n                if (!NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)) {\n                    throw error;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        try (HeapByteBufferArrayBaseOffsetRestorer ignored = HeapByteBufferArrayBaseOffsetRestorer.zeroOffset()) {\n            PlatformDependent.hasUnsafe();\n        }\n        exerciseInitializedPlatformDependent(PlatformDependent.class);\n        exerciseCachedDirectBufferConstructor(PlatformDependent.class.getClassLoader());"},{"oldText":"                byte expectedByteValue = 0x55;\n                invokeVoid(\n                        platformDependentClass,\n                        \"putByte\",\n                        new Class<?>[] {long.class, byte.class},\n                        memoryAddress,\n                        expectedByteValue\n                );\n                assertThat(invokeByte(\n                        platformDependentClass,\n                        \"getByte\",\n                        new Class<?>[] {long.class},\n                        memoryAddress\n                )).isEqualTo(expectedByteValue);\n            } finally {\n                invokeVoid(platformDependentClass, \"freeMemory\", new Class<?>[] {long.class}, memoryAddress);\n            }\n        } else {\n            assertThat(invokeBoolean(platformDependentClass, \"directBufferPreferred\")).isFalse();\n        }\n    }","newText":"                byte expectedByteValue = 0x55;\n                invokeVoid(\n                        platformDependentClass,\n                        \"putByte\",\n                        new Class<?>[] {long.class, byte.class},\n                        memoryAddress,\n                        expectedByteValue\n                );\n                assertThat(invokeByte(\n                        platformDependentClass,\n                        \"getByte\",\n                        new Class<?>[] {long.class},\n                        memoryAddress\n                )).isEqualTo(expectedByteValue);\n            } finally {\n                invokeVoid(platformDependentClass, \"freeMemory\", new Class<?>[] {long.class}, memoryAddress);\n            }\n\n            if (invokeBoolean(platformDependentClass, \"useDirectBufferNoCleaner\")) {\n                ByteBuffer noCleanerBuffer = (ByteBuffer) invoke(\n                        platformDependentClass,\n                        \"allocateDirectNoCleaner\",\n                        new Class<?>[] {int.class},\n                        Long.BYTES\n                );\n                try {\n                    assertThat(noCleanerBuffer.isDirect()).isTrue();\n                    assertThat(noCleanerBuffer.capacity()).isEqualTo(Long.BYTES);\n                    noCleanerBuffer.putLong(0, 0x0102030405060708L);\n                    assertThat(noCleanerBuffer.getLong(0)).isEqualTo(0x0102030405060708L);\n                } finally {\n                    invokeVoid(\n                            platformDependentClass,\n                            \"freeDirectNoCleaner\",\n                            new Class<?>[] {ByteBuffer.class},\n                            noCleanerBuffer\n                    );\n                }\n            }\n        } else {\n            assertThat(invokeBoolean(platformDependentClass, \"directBufferPreferred\")).isFalse();\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static void exerciseCachedDirectBufferConstructor(ClassLoader classLoader) throws Exception {\n        Class<?> platformDependent0Class = Class.forName(\n                \"io.netty.util.internal.PlatformDependent0\",\n                true,\n                classLoader\n        );\n        Constructor<?> replacementConstructor = DirectBufferConstructorProbe.class.getConstructor(\n                long.class,\n                int.class\n        );\n        Method newDirectBufferMethod = platformDependent0Class.getDeclaredMethod(\"newDirectBuffer\", long.class, int.class);\n        newDirectBufferMethod.setAccessible(true);\n\n        try (StaticFieldRestorer ignored = StaticFieldRestorer.replace(\n                platformDependent0Class,\n                \"DIRECT_BUFFER_CONSTRUCTOR\",\n                replacementConstructor\n        )) {\n            assertThatExceptionOfType(InvocationTargetException.class)\n                    .isThrownBy(() -> newDirectBufferMethod.invoke(null, 1L, 1))\n                    .satisfies(exception -> assertThat(exception.getCause()).isInstanceOf(Error.class));\n        }\n    }"},{"oldText":"    private static final class NettyIsolatedClassLoader extends URLClassLoader {","newText":"    public static final class DirectBufferConstructorProbe {\n        public DirectBufferConstructorProbe(long address, int capacity) {\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class NettyIsolatedClassLoader extends URLClassLoader {"},{"oldText":"    private static final class HeapByteBufferArrayBaseOffsetRestorer implements AutoCloseable {","newText":"    private static final class StaticFieldRestorer implements AutoCloseable {\n        private final Unsafe unsafe;\n        private final Object fieldBase;\n        private final long fieldOffset;\n        private final Object originalValue;\n\n        private StaticFieldRestorer(Unsafe unsafe, Object fieldBase, long fieldOffset, Object originalValue) {\n            this.unsafe = unsafe;\n            this.fieldBase = fieldBase;\n            this.fieldOffset = fieldOffset;\n            this.originalValue = originalValue;\n        }\n\n        private static StaticFieldRestorer replace(Class<?> owner, String fieldName, Object replacement)\n                throws ReflectiveOperationException {\n            Unsafe unsafe = HeapByteBufferArrayBaseOffsetRestorer.getUnsafe();\n            Field field = owner.getDeclaredField(fieldName);\n            Object fieldBase = unsafe.staticFieldBase(field);\n            long fieldOffset = unsafe.staticFieldOffset(field);\n            Object originalValue = unsafe.getObject(fieldBase, fieldOffset);\n            unsafe.putObject(fieldBase, fieldOffset, replacement);\n            return new StaticFieldRestorer(unsafe, fieldBase, fieldOffset, originalValue);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void close() {\n            unsafe.putObject(fieldBase, fieldOffset, originalValue);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class HeapByteBufferArrayBaseOffsetRestorer implements AutoCloseable {"}]}
